      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUC893d3bb8257f100580b98e32a097eed2"></a>Removal of the gear selector lever
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15134"> </a>Remove the oil sump guard (<a href="78006.html#DUCdebde6802aa910058bbaf20939ae18d2">Removing the oil sump guard</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15139"> </a>Drain the engine oil (<a href="77245.html#DUCc57ed0d029f510058c2bed44952c77d2">Changing engine oil and filter cartridge</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15144"> </a>Remove the sprocket cover (<a href="79974.html#DUC678e5bc82b2410058de4ee3905e05ec4">Removing the front sprocket</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15149"> </a>Remove the clutch slave cylinder (<a href="78738.html#DUC1e4714c82b2410058cedd30e2bfae6c4">Removing the clutch slave cylinder</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15154"> </a>Drain the cooling system (<a href="77257.html#DUCf34a5aa829f91005800d816ce97b3fd2">Changing the coolant</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15159"> </a>Remove the pump-cylinder hoses (<a href="45114.html#DUCad1f8410256a10058d3dd14d9928c7d2">Removing the cylinder/piston assembly</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15164"> </a>Remove the water pump/radiator pipes (<a href="44924.html#DUCc06658c8250110058a838a10427928d2">Removing cooling system pipes and unions</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15169"> </a>Remove the generator cover and the flywheel/generator unit (<a href="45174.html#DUCf616ff28259110058912eb60359b4bd2">Removing the generator cover</a>).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15175"> </a>Loosen and remove the fixing screws (1) and (2) of the complete gear selector lever (3) and collect the spacer (4).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15177"> </a>Remove the gearchange mechanism complete with the shaft, spring, and stop plate.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_032802062.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_032902063.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15184"> </a>Visually inspect the gear selector claw (5) for wear, particularly around the area where it contacts the selector drum.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15187"> </a>If it proves necessary to change components, disassemble the gear selector lever as shown in the exploded view. Reassemble
            the gear selector lever orienting the eccentric pin (6), suitably lubricated, in such a way that the lever arm (7) is positioned
            centrally with respect to the shoulders of the stop plate (8).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_033002064.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15192"> </a>Check that the spring (9) is installed correctly as shown in the figure.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_9_033102065.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e15197"> </a>Apply some specified grease and tighten nut (10) to 10 Nm (Min. 9 Nm - Max. 11 Nm).
         </div>
      </div>
